snippet.title: Statistics - Binomial Distributions
snippet.description:
Ready for a lesson on Binomial Distributions? Great, we are too! First though, we need to define it and understand how it works. Then we use it to explore the probability of several groups of people recognizing the brand McDonald's. What could be more important? YAY MATH! (HD)
